 "attached_info": "ClQIm6v9+uy+uJkYEAMaCDk5NzcxMjA0INTRlacGMAA4J0AYcgk2MTg3MDkyODR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1692954440.435333", "card_id": "Q_617980545", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「追求成熟这件事本身就不成熟」，你认同吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "怎样是成熟的？怎样是不成熟的？在我们的社会，有一套完整的话语体系去规训我们该做什么，不该做什么。《荒野对谈 2 》中，清华社会学副教授严飞这样说：追求成熟这件事本身就不成熟。你如何理解这句话？这里的成熟指的是什么？我们可以重新定义成熟吗？人一定要成熟吗？｜EP04 荒野会谈"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-6c672bc3f746f97dc1686db096347024_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/617980545"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIm6v9+uy+uJkYEAMaCDk5NjA5MTk3II6B/aYGMAA4J0AZcgk2MTc5ODA1NDV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1692954440.435808", "card_id": "Q_618909421", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有什么东西会让你觉得「提高了生活质量」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-5c33fc89ec97e1cdbba3505f61ff1200_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/618909421"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Im6v9+uy+uJkYEAMaCDk5ODE1NDkxIL2qm6cGMAA4KEAacgk2MTg5MDk0MjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1692954440.436042", "card_id": "Q_614122688", "feed_sp